Package org.eclipse.jdt.core.util

Interface IRuntimeVisibleAnnotationsAttribute

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IClassFileAttribute
    public interface IRuntimeVisibleAnnotationsAttribute
extends IClassFileAttribute
    Description of a runtime visible annotations attribute as described in the JVM specifications (added in J2SE 1.5). This interface may be implemented by clients.

    3.0
